Anker Soundcore P20i True Wireless Earbuds

Anker Soundcore P20i True Wireless Earbuds are a perfect blend of style and technology. Made from durable plastic, these earbuds offer a battery life of 10-30 hours, ensuring uninterrupted music experience. They come with sound isolating feature and two drivers for superior sound quality. The earbuds are charged using a charging case and have synthetic leather pads for comfortable wear. They support AAC and sbc codecs and have a Bluetooth version of 5.3. The package includes a user manual and a charging case. One of the key features of these earbuds is their waterproof nature, making them suitable for use in all weather conditions. They do not support memory cards but have an app for easy control. The earbuds have a resistance of 32Ω and a frequency response range of 20 - 20000Hz. They do not have active noise cancellation but come with volume control. The earbuds follow the dynamic vocalism principle and use Bluetooth for wireless communication. They have Type C connectors and are designed for in-ear use. The product is certified by CE, EAC, and FCC and is made in Mainland China. Get your Anker Soundcore P20i True Wireless Earbuds today at TechLand BD.

